  "body": "# Problem\r\nThere's a difference in actions available when viewing a image in full screen on Android and iOS.\r\n**iOS**: Context menu > `Save`, `Reply`, `View profile` (of sender)\r\n**Android**: `Save`\r\n\r\n![Frame 1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/130434710-1b9c942d-7b87-4edc-bd0f-56621d377ebd.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\n- Mimic iOS implementation on Android\r\n- Use native icons where relevant\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n`Reply` and `View profile` actions are also available on Android\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\n\r\n## Future Steps\r\nRelated issue to add Share action #12472 \r\n\r\n",
